<item>
            <title>[HBASE-2879] Offer ZK CLI outside of HBase Shell</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2879</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Although having the ZooKeeper CLI options in hbase shell is nice, we needed to have an easy way to access the ZK CLI outside of the shell (&quot;bin/hbase zkcli&quot;) in case the master is down.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12470195">HBASE-2879</key>
            <summary>Offer ZK CLI outside of HBase Shell</summary>
